sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as AAOS App
    participant Phone as Smartphone Browser
    participant Backend as Car Pay-in Backend
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant Hyundai as MyHyundai OAuth API
    participant DB as Car Pay-in DB

    User->>App: Start vehicle registration
    App->>App: Generate session_id and vin_hash
    App->>Backend: POST /auth/qr-session
    Backend->>Redis: Save qr_session:{session_id}
    Backend-->>App: Return login_url
    App-->>User: Show QR code with session_id

    User->>Phone: Scan QR code
    Phone->>Backend: GET /auth/hyundai/start
    Backend->>Redis: Read qr_session:{session_id}
    Backend->>Redis: Save oauth_state:{oauth_state}
    Backend-->>Phone: Redirect to MyHyundai OAuth

    Phone->>Hyundai: Login and consent
    Hyundai-->>Backend: Return authorization code
    Backend->>Hyundai: Exchange code for tokens
    Hyundai-->>Backend: Return Hyundai access and refresh tokens
    Backend->>Hyundai: Fetch profile and vehicle list with access token
    Hyundai-->>Backend: Return user and vehicle list

    Backend->>DB: UPSERT users
    Backend->>Backend: Discard Hyundai access and refresh tokens
    Backend->>Redis: Save hyundai_oauth:{session_id}
    Backend->>Redis: Save app_login_result:{session_id}
